Mauritius Credit to Private Industry Increased 1% in February

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-03-31T12:04:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/mauritius-credit-to-private-industry-increased-1-in-february.html
Commercial bank lending to private
industry in Mauritius rose 1 percent in February from a month
earlier, the central bank said in a statement on its website
today.  Total credit rose to 230.24 billion rupees from 228.02
billion rupees, the Port Louis-based bank said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in  Port Louis  via Johannesburg at 
1933 or  gbell16@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin in Johannesburg at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 